## ğŸš€ Quick Start (Production)

### 1. Launch Sofia Receptionist
```bash
cd /Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/sofia-hotel/agents/hotel
/Users/tolga/Desktop/elvi/sofia-pers/local-voice-ai-agent/.venv/bin/python sofia_hotel_receptionist.py receptionist
```

### 2. Expected Behavior
1. Sofia greets guest with voice
2. System listens for 5 seconds
3. Guest speaks hotel request
4. Sofia processes and responds with voice
5. Repeat until guest says "goodbye"

### 3. Guest Interaction Flow
```
Sofia: "Guten Tag! Welcome to Hotel LÃ¤rchenhof..."
ğŸ¤ Listening...
Guest: "I need a room for tonight"
